transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling. This is John. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: If it's calling about my account, it just – I don't want it to auto-fill. I want to be able to go on there and just pick when I need to get a prescription. How do I do that?

Speaker 1: Let me get you somebody to help you with that, sir. One second.

Speaker 2: All right.
